        <h2 class="section-heading">What We Look For</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">After analyzing dozens of online legal platforms, we found that service breadth, pricing transparency, and attorney access matter most to today's users:</p>
        <div class="criteria-grid">
          {criteria.map((item) => (
            <div class="criteria-card">
              <div class={`criteria-icon ${item.color}`}>
                {item.icon === 'shield' && (
